S.FORM: Kasasilsil no Sakowan no Rosiya(kuwaping a sowal: ) Ira ko 85 ko kasasiromaroma no sakowan no Rosiya: 3 ko mipatosokan no sakakaay sifo a mikowan a taokay( federal cities)o Mosko Si, Senpitopaw Si ato Sayfanpaw Si. 46 ko etal sakowan( oblasts, "provinces") 9 ko salawacan sakowan( krais, "territories") 22 ko niyahpikowan a kitakit( republics) 1 ko niyahpikowan( autonomous oblast, "autonomous province") 4 ko niyahpikowan a niyaro' ( autonomous okrugs, "autonomous districts")
